'''Nalros''' was the native [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Nalroni/Legends|Nalroni]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from the<ref name="POT" /> [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]]<ref name="TEA">''[[The Essential Atlas]]''</ref> [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Celanon/Legends|Celanon]]. The [[Protocol droid/Legends|protocol droid]] [[C-3PO/Legends|C-3PO]] could speak Nalros.<ref name="POT" />

==Known words==
*''dinn'' - "Small hard-shelled insects."<ref name="POT" />

==Behind the scenes==
Nalros was mentioned in [[Barbara Hambly]]'s [[1997]] novel ''[[Planet of Twilight]]''.<ref name="POT" />

